<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 16:09:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列改革运动请愿反对不教授核心课程的学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-reform-movement-petitions-against-schools-that-do-not-teach-core-curriculum/0000018d-3177-d81e-abdf-397f10b30000</link><description>以色列宗教行动中心提交了请愿书，涉及所谓“豁免”的极端正统机构，这些机构只需教授 55% 的核心课程</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 14:59:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-reform-movement-petitions-against-schools-that-do-not-teach-core-curriculum/0000018d-3177-d81e-abdf-397f10b30000</guid></item><item><title>“当他们在加沙死去时，你不会坐在这里”：人质家庭冲击以色列议会委员会会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/you-wont-sit-here-while-theyre-dying-hostage-families-storm-knesset-committee-meeting/0000018d-3110-d268-addd-3b7909ac0000</link><description>沙查尔·莫尔的叔叔在加沙被哈马斯关押，他呼吁摩西·加夫尼和其他以色列议会极端正统派议员离开政府</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 14:55:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/you-wont-sit-here-while-theyre-dying-hostage-families-storm-knesset-committee-meeting/0000018d-3110-d268-addd-3b7909ac0000</guid></item><item><title>两名东耶路撒冷居民因涉嫌在以色列议会附近策划受 ISIS 启发的恐怖阴谋而被起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/two-east-jerusalem-residents-indicted-for-aledged-isis-inspired-terror-plot-near-knesset/0000018d-318e-d268-addd-3bffc8a70000</link><description>根据起诉书，这两个人在网上被激进化并宣誓效忠伊斯兰国后，据称计划于 11 月在议会外炸毁一辆装满油箱的卡车。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 14:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/two-east-jerusalem-residents-indicted-for-aledged-isis-inspired-terror-plot-near-knesset/0000018d-318e-d268-addd-3bffc8a70000</guid></item><item><title>新民意调查显示，以色列人对拜登将巴勒斯坦国与释放人质、沙特关系正常化联系起来的计划持开放态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/poll-israelis-open-to-biden-plan-linking-palestinian-state-hostages-saudi-normalization/0000018d-3035-dd75-addd-f2f577900000</link><description>尽管人们假设以色列人自 10 月 7 日起就会向右转，但最近的一项民意调查显示，如果建立非军事化的巴勒斯坦国与释放人质和沙特关系正常化一起成为一揽子协议的一部分，大多数人将支持建立非军事化的巴勒斯坦国。这对拜登来说是个好消息</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 13:18:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/poll-israelis-open-to-biden-plan-linking-palestinian-state-hostages-saudi-normalization/0000018d-3035-dd75-addd-f2f577900000</guid></item><item><title>如果没有巴勒斯坦工人，以色列经济还能持续多久？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-wont-let-palestinian-workers-in-but-its-economy-needs-them-desperately/0000018d-2bda-dd75-addd-fbfb543a0000</link><description>自加沙战争开始以来，政府已对估计 120,000 名巴勒斯坦工人关闭了大门，但尚未提出用外国工人取代他们的计划 ■ 与此同时，失去相当一部分劳动力的企业主正在付出代价</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 13:15:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-wont-let-palestinian-workers-in-but-its-economy-needs-them-desperately/0000018d-2bda-dd75-addd-fbfb543a0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，数十名巴勒斯坦人在汗尤尼斯的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/idf-deepens-khan-yunis-invasion-palestinians-report-dozens-killed-including-children/0000018d-30c4-d81e-abdf-38ccc2c20000</link><description>巴勒斯坦红新月会反驳说，以色列国防军阻止他们到达被轰炸的地区，包括医疗中心。以色列军队表示，部队“继续打击汗尤尼斯地区的恐怖分子目标”</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 13:04:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/idf-deepens-khan-yunis-invasion-palestinians-report-dozens-killed-including-children/0000018d-30c4-d81e-abdf-38ccc2c20000</guid></item><item><title>你会让你的孩子参加内塔尼亚胡的战争吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/would-you-send-your-child-to-fight-in-netanyahus-war/0000018d-30a6-dd75-addd-f2e7ec590000</link><description>每个人都必须问自己，他们是否会去对抗哈马斯，或者将他们的孩子送去参加这场他们可能一去不复返的战争</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 11:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/would-you-send-your-child-to-fight-in-netanyahus-war/0000018d-30a6-dd75-addd-f2e7ec590000</guid></item><item><title>他被绑架到加沙并被以色列士兵杀害。他的乐队成员为他而演奏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-01-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bandmates-of-israeli-drummer-kidnapped-by-hamas-and-killed-by-idf-play-on-in-his-honor/0000018d-2bea-dd75-addd-fbeb4ef90000</link><description>10 月 7 日 Yotam Haim 被哈马斯绑架的那天，他和他的金属核乐队 Persephore 即将举行他们有史以来最盛大的演出。他的乐队成员回忆起一位敏感的鼓手，他教会他们要有远大的梦想，同时成功地战胜了内心的恶魔</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 11:38:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-01-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bandmates-of-israeli-drummer-kidnapped-by-hamas-and-killed-by-idf-play-on-in-his-honor/0000018d-2bea-dd75-addd-fbeb4ef90000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高级外交官在部长会议上表示，以色列摧毁哈马斯的计划不起作用，需要进行和平谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-plan-to-destroy-hamas-not-working-peace-talks-needed-top-eu-diplomat-says/0000018d-3086-dd75-addd-f2e732620000</link><description>欧盟领导人在布鲁塞尔外长会议上加大了要求两国解决方案的压力。欧盟外交政策负责人表示，他打算推动一项国际进程，以建立与以色列共存的巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 10:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-plan-to-destroy-hamas-not-working-peace-talks-needed-top-eu-diplomat-says/0000018d-3086-dd75-addd-f2e732620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和加沙，几年后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-gaza-a-few-years-from-now/0000018d-3087-db77-ad9f-ffb726a00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 10:21:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-gaza-a-few-years-from-now/0000018d-3087-db77-ad9f-ffb726a00000</guid></item><item><title>在巨大分歧中，以色列和哈马斯表示准备在长期僵局后讨论加沙人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/pressure-on-the-israeli-government-to-reach-a-hostage-deal-is-mounting/0000018d-2d34-daf5-a1bf-ad74342e0000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，预计本周将在开罗重启谈判。这也表明哈马斯在加沙和海外的领导层之间的争端日益加剧 ■ 内塔尼亚胡与拜登的擦肩而过，实际上有利于总理赢回右翼选票的努力</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 04:01:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/pressure-on-the-israeli-government-to-reach-a-hostage-deal-is-mounting/0000018d-2d34-daf5-a1bf-ad74342e0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党面临压力，要求就结束以色列-加沙战争进行撤军谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/pressure-on-hezbollah-increases-but-successful-negotiations-of-its-withdrawal-are-far-off/0000018d-2e77-daf5-a1bf-ae77b1430000</link><description>真主党意识到与以色列的大规模战争不符合其政治利益，因为它仍然坚定地认为，必须与以色列达成协议才能全面结束加沙战争。然而参与谈判的五国却没有任何筹码</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 04:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/pressure-on-hezbollah-increases-but-successful-negotiations-of-its-withdrawal-are-far-off/0000018d-2e77-daf5-a1bf-ae77b1430000</guid></item><item><title>拒绝哈马斯条件第二天，内塔尼亚胡向以色列人质家庭表示：“哈马斯缺乏真正的建议”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article-live/after-day-break-rocket-sirens-sound-in-israels-northern-border-with-lebanon/0000018d-2f22-daf5-a1bf-af7274840000</link><description>以色列政界人士周一连续召开党内会议，工党的不信任动议在无需多数票的情况下获得通过，推翻政府 ■ 黎巴嫩议会议长表示“我们绝不能按照时间表卷入与以色列的战争” ■ 欧盟外交政策负责人称以色列摧毁哈马斯的计划行不通，需要和平谈判 ■ 由于以色列国防军在汗尤尼斯的活动，数千名加沙人撤离到拉法 ■ 数十名被扣押在加沙的人质家属扰乱议会会议</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 03:31:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article-live/after-day-break-rocket-sirens-sound-in-israels-northern-border-with-lebanon/0000018d-2f22-daf5-a1bf-af7274840000</guid></item><item><title>选择在西岸学习的以色列阿拉伯人数量正在下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/the-number-of-israeli-arabs-choosing-to-study-in-the-west-bank-is-declining/0000018d-2e2a-db77-ad9f-ff3a998a0000</link><description>财政部将这一变化归因于通过津贴和预科课程鼓励阿拉伯学生到以色列学习的努力，以及获得非以色列认可机构学位的卫生专业工作越来越困难。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 23:27:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/the-number-of-israeli-arabs-choosing-to-study-in-the-west-bank-is-declining/0000018d-2e2a-db77-ad9f-ff3a998a0000</guid></item><item><title>“放弃责任”：法院裁定以色列政府未能促进回收竞争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/abandoned-its-responsibility-court-rules-govt-failed-to-enable-recycling-competition/0000018d-2d80-dd75-addd-ffe1af8e0000</link><description>法院对一家回收公司提交的请愿书作出的判决称，环保部未履行其法律责任，并责令其成立专门的工作组并改变其政策</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 20:42:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/abandoned-its-responsibility-court-rules-govt-failed-to-enable-recycling-competition/0000018d-2d80-dd75-addd-ffe1af8e0000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列的所有批评都是威胁时，每一位左翼教师都是叛徒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-21/ty-article/.highlight/when-all-criticism-in-israel-is-a-threat-every-leftist-teacher-is-a-traitor/0000018d-2d13-db77-ad9f-ff33b7370000</link><description>导致一名 16 岁女孩希望老师得癌症的内心仇恨并非诞生于 10 月 7 日，也不会在最后一支部队离开加沙时消散</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 19:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-21/ty-article/.highlight/when-all-criticism-in-israel-is-a-threat-every-leftist-teacher-is-a-traitor/0000018d-2d13-db77-ad9f-ff33b7370000</guid></item><item><title>两名真主党成员在黎巴嫩南部据称被以色列无人机袭击身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/two-hezbollah-members-killed-in-alleged-israeli-drone-strike-in-southern-lebanon/0000018d-2d4d-db77-ad9f-ff7f67350000</link><description>这次袭击造成一名真主党成员死亡，七人受伤，其中包括一名情况危急的妇女，据称是以色列在黎巴嫩定点清除战略转变的一部分。真主党证实其一名成员被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 19:16:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/two-hezbollah-members-killed-in-alleged-israeli-drone-strike-in-southern-lebanon/0000018d-2d4d-db77-ad9f-ff7f67350000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发布备忘录解释为何对以色列发动战争；加沙人质疑时机，批评哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/hamas-releases-memo-explaining-why-it-waged-war-on-israel-gazans-question-timing/0000018d-2d3a-db77-ad9f-ff3abfd30000</link><description>该文件声称，这次致命袭击是为了阻止西岸的犹太化并结束对加沙的封锁。该文件发布的时间引发了疑问：加沙的消息人士，包括那些认同哈马斯的消息人士表示，哈马斯正在应对对加沙人付出的沉重代价的批评</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 19:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/hamas-releases-memo-explaining-why-it-waged-war-on-israel-gazans-question-timing/0000018d-2d3a-db77-ad9f-ff3abfd30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：疑似被俘的以色列士兵于 10 月 7 日被杀，其尸体被扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-israeli-soldier-thought-to-be-captured-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-held-in-gaza/0000018d-2d10-dd75-addd-fff189690000</link><description>以色列军方确定，19岁的职业排球运动员谢伊·莱文森于10月7日在装甲旅服役时身亡。他现在被正式视为被恐怖组织关押的阵亡士兵</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 18:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-israeli-soldier-thought-to-be-captured-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-held-in-gaza/0000018d-2d10-dd75-addd-fff189690000</guid></item><item><title>沙特外长：如果不与巴勒斯坦国建立正常关系，以色列就没有正常关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/saudi-foreign-minister-no-normal-israel-ties-without-path-to-palestinian-state/0000018d-2cdb-dd75-addd-fefbe8550000</link><description>沙特外长费萨尔·本·法尔汉·阿勒沙特亲王声称利雅得将承认以色列作为更广泛政治协议的一部分，几天后明确表示，只有通过“解决巴勒斯坦问题”才能实现地区稳定</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 16:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-21/ty-article/.premium/saudi-foreign-minister-no-normal-israel-ties-without-path-to-palestinian-state/0000018d-2cdb-dd75-addd-fefbe8550000</guid></item></channel></rss>